{"tid":1829353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有沒人打算更進一步 （運動提議）","createTime":"2020-01-18T16:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T07:44:49.000Z","uid":156828,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"17c0ec64c60c7d59ee98d95a9a0888dd89d38759","tid":1829353,"uid":156828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:09:20.000Z","msg":"每次和平集會，遊行班狗都阻撓、濫捕<br />\n<br />\n同時 間唔中都有手足問點解唔各區開花，如果要再進一步 可唔可以勇武手足去自己屋企附近區 快閃開花<br />\n<br />\n就算唔多區集會，都可以集中幾區集會<br />\n<br />\n現在遊行集會只係固定劇本，聽日都只會係濫捕，腰斬<br />\n<br />\n其實點做都會比人屌送頭，可唔可以試下唔同方向"},{"pid":"00d98e650f4e43b19f1bd637952f4dbb2272a6cc","tid":1829353,"uid":156828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:09:31.000Z","msg":"1/5"},{"pid":"68bd219c6e0f1063439a38dd9af8e64a8f8bc8b8","tid":1829353,"uid":82746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:09:43.000Z","msg":"個熱門似咩樣呀！同我推1.19遊行post -  <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1822966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1822966</a>"},{"pid":"b68879991276864ea1236aacd59e2ea4edda95b9","tid":1829353,"uid":156828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:09:49.000Z","msg":"2/5"},{"pid":"046ba1486deb267684bdf6dfd9292330a3b224b4","tid":1829353,"uid":156828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:10:18.000Z","msg":"3/5"},{"pid":"8fa283f106f29712deef19130f5c1d16fc24877a","tid":1829353,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53f4dAb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F53f4dAb.gif&h=755d7b56&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6e7e62dc2dcfd1cb968444dddaefe5b14223c66","tid":1829353,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:13:19.000Z","msg":"有格林機槍就可以控制街道"},{"pid":"39d19de727d56f8e9add642200d0bb2dab245ebc","tid":1829353,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:13:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>廢功組 真普選！ </strong></span>"},{"pid":"21625e1b153d1e17ac2e2e1712076351f85bea10","tid":1829353,"uid":156828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:16:01.000Z","msg":"1/5"},{"pid":"af58fb6942fe68a6675f13ddc72c399e229fd4dd","tid":1829353,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:19:33.000Z","msg":"其實都講好多個月。<br />\n大概由十月開始講，<br />\n但真係好似無成過事，<br />\n可能怕無街坊做哨。"},{"pid":"018baab870a8631a63f2edd12eecda8c0c15e62c","tid":1829353,"uid":156828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"af58fb6942fe68a6675f13ddc72c399e229fd4dd","tid":1829353,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:19:33.000Z","msg":"其實都講好多個月。<br />\n大概由十月開始講，<br />\n但真係好似無成過事，<br />\n可能怕無街坊做哨。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:21:26.000Z","msg":"就係因為沒試過，先應該試"},{"pid":"373b204a46051e7e988db46aa63d2456430dae5d","tid":1829353,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GmwK5WU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGmwK5WU.jpg&h=18813d78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8a1db3f10a692331cfd0c5dd0895a77be595601","tid":1829353,"uid":156828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:28:09.000Z","msg":"1/5"},{"pid":"c50b0a7424eb065cd06fcb205995258f90cf4563","tid":1829353,"uid":55083,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:39:58.000Z","msg":"遊擊一早就有人講 但係無人做<br />\n係都要搵公開哂時間地點嘅集會遊行<br />\n唔俾人重點打就假<br />\n依家仲要周圍都係鬼 又唔捉/捉完唔做野<br />\n(唔捉鬼唔係因為唔應該捉 係因為捉完都無後果 自然捉極都有)<br />\n佢地自己group自己都唔肯定有無<br />\n依家勇武肯定愈黎愈少 咁落去肯定玩完<br />\n<br />\n呢個幾兩個月就係話俾人聽<br />\n你一stop反抗就清算<br />\nd人仲以為嬴個無實權嘅區議會就反cup<br />\n根本唔脫離現有制度就無可能嬴<br />\n偏偏大部份人都無諗住改革個制度"},{"pid":"4b6f9dafe017475b2ee0756cc2017bb73a4f0947","tid":1829353,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1